flowchart TB
  CLI[tet_cli<br/>standalone CLI] --> RUNTIME[tet_runtime<br/>Tet facade · OTP runtime]
  WEB[tet_web_phoenix<br/>optional LiveView adapter] --> RUNTIME
  RUNTIME --> CORE[tet_core<br/>domain · policies · behaviours]

  STORE_MEM[tet_store_memory<br/>tests] --> CORE
  STORE_SQL[tet_store_sqlite<br/>default local] --> CORE
  STORE_PG[tet_store_postgres<br/>optional server] --> CORE

  RUNTIME -. uses configured store .-> STORE_MEM
  RUNTIME -. uses configured store .-> STORE_SQL
  RUNTIME -. uses configured store .-> STORE_PG

  PHX[Phoenix/LiveView deps<br/>web only] -. allowed only in .-> WEB

  FORBID1[forbidden: core -> runtime/web/Phoenix/Ecto]
  FORBID2[forbidden: runtime -> Phoenix/Plug/TetWeb]
  FORBID3[forbidden: CLI -> web/store/runtime internals]

  CORE -. must not .-> FORBID1
  RUNTIME -. must not .-> FORBID2
  CLI -. must not .-> FORBID3
